6:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Amie and ClickUp AI share a solid foundation of core features including Task Management, Ai Assistant, Calendar, Collaboration. On the other hand, ClickUp AI uniquely offers Notes and Automation and Templates and Analytics, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Amie holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10, while ClickUp AI scores 8/10 overall and 6/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Amie and ClickUp AI offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Amie's free tier and ClickUp AI's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
