a:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Amie is best suited for professionals, freelancers, calendar power users, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. ClickUp AI, meanwhile, shines for project managers, agencies, growing teams, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2020, Amie describes itself as \"Joyful calendar app combining scheduling, tasks, and availability sharing.\" ClickUp AI, established in 2017, positions itself as \"All-in-one productivity platform with role-based AI writing and task management.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
b:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **ClickUp AI** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (8.0 vs 7.0), more features (10 vs 6), availability of a free plan. However, this does not mean Amie is a poor choice — far from it. Amie excels in its own right, particularly for professionals and freelancers.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value extremely feature-rich platform, go with ClickUp AI. If beautiful and joyful design matters more to you, Amie is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
